data.description: Beautifully appointed and maintained home in a quiet Wylie neighborhood. 3810 Enchanted Rock offers 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms in a wonderful split floor plan design. The secluded master features a fabulous ensuite with a large wraparound walk-in closet, separate shower and dual sinks. The living area is warm and inviting with lots of open space to accommodate many large furniture configurations and a gorgeous fireplace. The kitchen provides ample granite counterspace, many beautiful cabinets for storage with a large island, a double oven and the most amazingly large walk-in pantry. Stainless steel fridge also conveys! Stepping out back, you are greeted with an oversized covered patio ready for those summer night gatherings and cook outs. Lots to love about this house! Seller says swing set in backyard stays as well!
